 <div class="table-responsive"> 
  <table class="wiki_table"> 
   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Gavel of Haima</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" title="Gavel of Haima" src="/file/Elden-Ring/gavel_of_haima_sorcery_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="gavel of haima sorcery elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Glintstone Sorceries" href="/Glintstone+Sorceries" target="">Glintstone Sorceries</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost 22</td> 
     <td>Slots Used 1</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Attacks using a magic greathammer 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Intelligence" href="/Intelligence" target="">Intelligence</a> 25 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith" target="">Faith</a>&nbsp;0 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arcane" href="/Arcane" target="">Arcane</a>&nbsp;0 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Gavel of Haima</strong> is a&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sorceries" href="/Sorceries" target="">Sorcery</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Gavel of Haima spell</strong> creates a magical weapon that strikes enemies from above. Updated to <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>One of the glintstone sorceries of the Academy of Raya Lucaria.<br><br>Creates a magical greathammer and slams it down.<br>Allows one follow-up attack.<br><br>Drawn from the scholarly conspectus of Haima, the adjudicator of the academy, this sorcery employs might as a means to quell conflict.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Gavel of Haima</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Gavel of Haima</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li> <p>Can be found in the chest at the top of the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Converted Fringe Tower" href="/Converted+Fringe+Tower" target="">Converted Fringe Tower</a> in the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Liurnia of the Lakes" href="/Liurnia+of+the+Lakes" target="">Liurnia of the Lakes</a> region. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=1868&amp;lat=-120.384375&amp;lng=82.111581&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=1868&amp;lat=-120.384375&amp;lng=82.111581&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>. It requires the&nbsp;Erudition gesture to unlock:</p> <p><sub>Give Thops the Academy Glintstone Key (Used to gain access to Converted Towers)</sub></p> <p>&nbsp;</p> </li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Gavel of Haima Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Glintstone Sorceries" href="/Glintstone+Sorceries">Glintstone Sorcery</a></li> 
 <li>Stamina Cost:&nbsp;38</li> 
 <li>Deals magic damage</li> 
 <li>Has very good stance-breaking capabilities</li> 
 <li>If dual wielding staves, you can bypass the single follow-up attack and chain this repeatedly by casting from one hand and then the other, alternating each time.&nbsp;</li> 
 <li><span style="color: #ff6600;"><em>Note:</em></span> As of <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>, FP cost reduced from 25&nbsp;to 22, the hammer portion of the attack now deals increased damage and the attack does more stamina damage against guarding enemies. In addition, stamina cost was reduced from 46 to 38.</li> 
</ul> 
