<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Gavel of Haima&nbsp;Note and Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Updated to patch&nbsp;<strong>1.07</strong>. See&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes" target="">Patch Notes</a>&nbsp;for details.</li> 
 <li>Other notes and player tips go here.&nbsp;</li> 
</ul> 
